<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Hero Banner Styles */
        .main-hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 50%, #60a5fa 100%);
            padding: 80px 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .main-hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1000 100"><path d="M0,100 L1000,50 L1000,100 Z" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/></svg>') no-repeat bottom;
            background-size: cover;
        }
        
        .hero-banner {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        
        .hero-text-content {
            color: white;
            flex: 1;
            padding-right: 50px;
        }
        
        .hero-text-content h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }
        
        .hero-text-content h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .hero-text-content h3 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .hero-text-content .collection {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .hero-models {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .model-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            min-width: 200px;
        }
        
        .model-card img {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }
        
        .model-card h4 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .model-card p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        
        /* News Section */
        .news-section {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background: #f8fafc;
        }
        
        .news-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        
        .news-carousel {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            padding: 20px 0;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }
        
        .news-card {
            min-width: 350px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .news-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        
        .news-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        
        .news-card-content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .news-card-content h4 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #1e3a8a;
        }
        
        .news-card-content p {
            color: #64748b;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        /* Shop Section */
        .shop-section {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background: white;
        }
        
        .shop-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding: 0 20px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
        }
        
        .shop-title {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .shop-title .blue-bar {
            width: 4px;
            height: 40px;
            background: #3b82f6;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }
        
        .shop-title h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1e3a8a;
        }
        
        .shop-title p {
            color: #64748b;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        
        .shop-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 40px;
        }
        
        .shop-banner-left {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .shop-banner-left img {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            object-fit: cover;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .shop-banner-left h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .shop-banner-right {
            flex: 1;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #b91c1c 100%);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .shop-banner-right h3 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .shop-banner-right img {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            margin: 0 auto 15px;
        }
        
        /* Products Section */
        .products-section {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff 0%, #e0f2fe 100%);
        }
        
        .products-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        
        .products-carousel {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            padding: 20px 0;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }
        
        .product-card {
            min-width: 300px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .product-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        
        .product-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: 15px;
            left: 15px;
            background: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .product-image {
            height: 280px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .product-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            z-index: 1;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .product-content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .product-content h4 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .product-content .price {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #dc2626;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .product-features {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .product-features li {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            padding-left: 15px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .product-features li::before {
            content: '✓';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #10b981;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        /* Nút mua hàng */
        .product-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .btn-buy-now {
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: background 0.3s;
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .btn-buy-now:hover {
            background: #0056b3;
        }
        
        .btn-add-cart {
            background: #28a745;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: background 0.3s;
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .btn-add-cart:hover {
            background: #1e7e34;
        }
        
        .btn-buy-now:disabled,
        .btn-add-cart:disabled {
            background: #6c757d;
            cursor: not-allowed;
        }
        
        /* Navigation arrows */
        .carousel-nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .nav-arrow {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .nav-arrow:hover {
            background: #1e3a8a;
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        
        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-banner {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            
            .hero-text-content {
                padding-right: 0;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }
            
            .hero-text-content h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            
            .hero-text-content h2 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
            
            .hero-models {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
            }
            
            .model-card {
                min-width: 150px;
            }
            
            .shop-banner {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            
            .news-carousel,
            .products-carousel {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .news-card,
            .product-card {
                min-width: 280px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <!-- Original Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <div class="hero-left">
                    <div class="hero-images">
                        <div class="image-grid">
                            <div class="image-item stylist">
                                <img src="/images/stylist.jpg" alt="Stylist">
                            </div>
                            <div class="image-item client-1">
                                <img src="/images/client-1.jpg" alt="Client 1">
                            </div>
                            <div class="image-item client-2">
                                <img src="/images/client-2.jpg" alt="Client 2">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="badge">
                            <div class="badge-content">
                                <span class="badge-text">Designed By Hair Stylist Masters</span>
                                <div class="badge-center">
                                    <h3>LYN Salon</h3>
                                    <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-right">
                    <div class="hero-logo">
                        <h1>LYN Salon</h1>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hero-text">
                        <h2>UỐN NHUỘM THIẾT KẾ</h2>
                        <h2>PHỤC HỒI CHUYÊN SÂU</h2>
                        <h2>LIPID BOND 2025</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hero-features">
                        <div class="feature-tag">3IN1</div>
                        <ul class="feature-list">
                            <li>TÓC KHỎE TRONG MƯỢT NGOÀI</li>
                            <li>TIẾT KIỆM THỜI GIAN CHỌN KIỂU VÀ CHĂM SÓC</li>
                            <li>SÁNG BỪNG NGŨ QUAN - RỘNG ĐƯỜNG TÀI LỘC</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-indicators">
                <span class="indicator active"></span>
                <span class="indicator"></span>
                <span class="indicator"></span>
                <span class="indicator"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- DỊCH VỤ TÓC Section -->
    <section class="services">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">DỊCH VỤ TÓC</h2>
            <div class="services-grid">
                <% services.filter(service => 
                    service.name.toLowerCase().includes('cắt tóc') || 
                    service.name.toLowerCase().includes('thay đổi màu') || 
                    service.name.toLowerCase().includes('uốn') ||
                    service.name.toLowerCase().includes('nhuộm') ||
                    service.name.toLowerCase().includes('duỗi')
                ).forEach(function(service) { %>
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <div class="service-image">
                            <img src="<%= service.image_url || '/images/service-default.jpg' %>" alt="<%= service.name %>">
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-content">
                            <h3><%= service.name %></h3>
                            <p class="price">Giá từ <%= service.price.toLocaleString('vi-VN') %>VNĐ</p>
                            <a href="/services" class="learn-more">Tìm hiểu thêm ></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- THƯ GIÃN VÀ CHĂM SÓC DA Section -->
    <section class="relaxation">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">THƯ GIÃN VÀ CHĂM SÓC DA</h2>
            <div class="relaxation-grid">
                <% services.filter(service => 
                    service.name.toLowerCase().includes('gội dưỡng') || 
                    service.name.toLowerCase().includes('lấy ráy') ||
                    service.name.toLowerCase().includes('massage') ||
                    service.name.toLowerCase().includes('chăm sóc da') ||
                    service.name.toLowerCase().includes('thư giãn')
                ).forEach(function(service) { %>
                    <div class="relaxation-card">
                        <div class="relaxation-image">
                            <img src="<%= service.image_url || '/images/service-default.jpg' %>" alt="<%= service.name %>">
                        </div>
                        <div class="relaxation-content">
                            <h3><%= service.name %></h3>
                            <p class="price">Giá từ <%= service.price.toLocaleString('vi-VN') %>VNĐ</p>
                            <a href="/services" class="learn-more">Tìm hiểu thêm ></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Booking Section -->
    <section class="booking-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="booking-content">
                <div class="booking-card">
                    <h3>ĐẶT LỊCH GIỮ CHỖ CHỈ 30 GIÂY</h3>
                    <p>Cắt xong trả tiền, hủy lịch không sao</p>
                    <form class="booking-form" action="/book-appointment" method="GET">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="tel" placeholder="Nhập SĐT để đặt lịch" required>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">ĐẶT LỊCH NGAY</button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="review-card">
                    <h3>MỜI ANH ĐÁNH GIÁ CHẤT LƯỢNG PHỤC VỤ</h3>
                    <p>Phản hồi của anh sẽ giúp chúng em cải thiện chất lượng dịch vụ tốt hơn</p>
                    <div class="rating">
                        <i class="fas fa-star filled"></i>
                        <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                        <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                        <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                        <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Hero Banner -->
    <section class="main-hero">
        <div class="hero-banner">
            <div class="hero-text-content">
                <div class="collection">I SHINE COLLECTION - 'VIBE' NÀO CŨNG TOẢ SÁNG</div>
                <h1>TREND HAIR</h1>
                <h2>MEN</h2>
                <h2>HAIRSTYLE</h2>
                <h3>AW 25-26</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-models">
                <div class="model-card">
                    <img src="/images/model1.jpg" alt="Model 2" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/120x120/1e3a8a/ffffff?text=Model+2'">
                    <h4>Kiểu tóc hiện đại</h4>
                    <p>Phong cách nam tính</p>
                </div>
                <div class="model-card">
                    <img src="/images/model2.jpg" alt="Model 2" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/120x120/1e3a8a/ffffff?text=Model+2'">
                    <h4>Undercut phong cách</h4>
                    <p>Thời trang & nổi bật</p>
                </div>
                <div class="model-card">
                    <img src="/images/model3.jpg" alt="Model 3" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/120x120/60a5fa/ffffff?text=Model+3'">
                    <h4>Fade đẹp mắt</h4>
                    <p>Chuyên nghiệp</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content Blocks Section -->
    <section class="content-blocks" style="padding: 60px 0; background: white;">
        <div class="container">
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 30px;">
                <div class="content-block" style="background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                    <img src="/images/brother-collection.jpg" alt="Bộ sưu tập anh trai" style="width: 100%; height: 200px; object-fit: cover;" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/3b82f6/ffffff?text=Bộ+sưu+tập+anh+trai'">
                    <div style="padding: 20px;">
                        <h3 style="color: #1e3a8a; font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 10px;">BỘ SƯU TẬP ANH TRAI SAY HAIR</h3>
                        <p style="color: #64748b;">Phong cách nam tính, hiện đại và đầy cá tính</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="content-block" style="background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                    <img src="/images/k-perm.jpg" alt="K-Perm Ready" style="width: 100%; height: 200px; object-fit: cover;" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/1e3a8a/ffffff?text=K-PERM+READY'">
                    <div style="padding: 20px;">
                        <h3 style="color: #1e3a8a; font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 10px;">BTS K-PERM READY for NEW GAME</h3>
                        <p style="color: #64748b;">Kiểu tóc uốn đẹp, phong cách Hàn Quốc</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="content-block" style="background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                    <img src="/images/bad-boy.jpg" alt="Bad Boy Style" style="width: 100%; height: 200px; object-fit: cover;" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/60a5fa/ffffff?text=BAD+BOY'">
                    <div style="padding: 20px;">
                        <h3 style="color: #1e3a8a; font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 10px;">BAD BOY</h3>
                        <p style="color: #64748b;">Phong cách cá tính, mạnh mẽ và nổi bật</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- News Section -->
    <section class="news-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="news-title">TIN TỨC VỀ LYN SALON</h2>
            <div class="news-carousel">
                <div class="news-card">
                    <img src="/images/news1.jpg" alt="CEO LYN Salon" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/350x200/3b82f6/ffffff?text=CEO+LYN+Salon'">
                    <div class="news-card-content">
                        <h4>CEO LYN Salon kể chuyện từ bỏ công nghiệp hóa tay nghề stylist</h4>
                        <p>Khẳng định không phải cứ có tiền là muốn làm gì cũng được, chất lượng vẫn là ưu tiên hàng đầu...</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="news-card">
                    <img src="/images/news2.jpg" alt="LYN Salon Building" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/350x200/1e3a8a/ffffff?text=LYN+Salon+Building'">
                    <div class="news-card-content">
                        <h4>LYN Salon đặt mục tiêu 100 triệu USD doanh thu vào 2028</h4>
                        <p>Chuỗi salon tóc nam hàng đầu Việt Nam với định hướng phát triển bền vững và chất lượng...</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="news-card">
                    <img src="/images/news3.jpg" alt="Training Session" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/350x200/60a5fa/ffffff?text=Training+Session'">
                    <div class="news-card-content">
                        <h4>Thói quen bình thường tạo ra những điều phi thường ở LYN Salon</h4>
                        <p>Quy trình đào tạo chuyên nghiệp và cam kết chất lượng dịch vụ hàng đầu...</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="news-card">
                    <img src="/images/news4.jpg" alt="Hair Styling" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/350x200/3b82f6/ffffff?text=Hair+Styling'">
                    <div class="news-card-content">
                        <h4>Chuỗi cắt tóc nam với 1000+ khách hàng tìm đường</h4>
                        <p>Dịch vụ chất lượng cao với đội ngũ stylist chuyên nghiệp và tận tâm...</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
